Recommends: uwsgi, nginx
Description: An alternative web panel for Sensu.
 Hourglass aims to be a dashboard for the Sensu monitoring framework that has some features that the base dashboard (Uchiwa) is lacking
 .
 The Hourglass back-end is written in Python and uses the Flask framework. The front-end uses Bootstrap, jQuery, DataTables and many others

